init_text: Humans once wielded formidable magical power. But with over 7 billion of us on the planet now, Mana has spread far too thinly to have any effect. When hostile aliens reduce humanity to a mere fraction, the survivors discover an old power has begun to reawaken once again.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The survivors had to learn to live with the new world they found themselves in.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: They had to rebuild from scratch.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: But then, a few people began to notice something.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: It was a slow process, but the survivors began to realize that they were no longer completely helpless.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: And so, the survivors began to rebuild.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: But the survivors began to rebuild in a very different way.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The survivors began to call themselves "The Folk".

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: They had been expecting a primitive world, but instead they found a world that was a mix of fantasy and science fiction.
